<i>pouncy fun, fun, fun, fun, fun</i>

519
00:36:45,203 --> 00:36:47,967
<i>But the most wonderful thing</i>
<i>about tiggers is I'm the only one</i>

520
00:36:48,039 --> 00:36:50,132
<i>I'm the only one</i>

521
00:36:54,545 --> 00:36:57,480
Well, if what Tigger said was true...

522
00:36:57,548 --> 00:37:01,143
and there really were
"heffalumps" and "woozles" about...

523
00:37:01,219 --> 00:37:04,154
there was only
one thing to do:

524
00:37:04,222 --> 00:37:08,181
Take drastic precautions
to protect his precious honey.

525
00:37:15,499 --> 00:37:17,967
Oh, hello.

526
00:37:18,035 --> 00:37:23,496
Am I glad to see you.
It's more friendly with two.

527
00:37:23,574 --> 00:37:26,600
Now, you go that way...

528
00:37:26,677 --> 00:37:28,702
and l'll go this way.

529
00:37:33,584 --> 00:37:36,212
You didn't see anything, did you?

530
00:37:36,287 --> 00:37:38,949
Neither did I.

531
00:37:40,424 --> 00:37:42,619
Now, the very blustery night...

532
00:37:42,693 --> 00:37:45,025
turned into a very rainy night...

533
00:37:45,096 --> 00:37:47,690
and Pooh kept his lonely vigil...

534
00:37:47,765 --> 00:37:51,997
hour after hour after hour.

535
00:37:52,069 --> 00:37:54,128
Until, at last...

536
00:37:54,205 --> 00:37:58,574
Pooh fell fast asleep
and began to dream.

537
00:38:03,214 --> 00:38:05,808
"Heffalumps" and "woozles."

538
00:38:05,883 --> 00:38:10,650
"Heffalumps" and "woozles" steal honey.

539
00:38:10,721 --> 00:38:14,487
Beware. Beware.

540
00:38:14,558 --> 00:38:16,549
<i>They're black, they're brown</i>
<i>They're up, they're down</i>

541
