<i>A "heffalump"or "woozle's"</i>
<i>very sly, sly, sly, sly</i>

547
00:38:34,845 --> 00:38:38,576
<i>They come in ones and "twosles"</i>
<i>but if they so "choosles"</i>

548
00:38:38,649 --> 00:38:42,779
<i>Before your eyes you'll see them</i>
<i>multiply, ply, ply, ply</i>

549
00:38:42,853 --> 00:38:46,687
<i>They're extraordinary</i>
<i>so better be wary</i>

550
00:38:46,757 --> 00:38:50,716
<i>Because they come in every</i>
<i>shape and size, size, size, size</i>

551
00:38:50,795 --> 00:38:54,424
<i>If honey's what you covet</i>
<i>you'll find that they love it</i>

552
00:38:54,498 --> 00:38:58,366
<i>Because they guzzle up</i>
<i>the thing you prize</i>

553
00:38:58,436 --> 00:39:00,700
<i>They're green, they're blue</i>
<i>They're pink, they're white</i>

554
00:39:00,771 --> 00:39:02,932
<i>They're round, they're square</i>
<i>They're a terrible sight</i>

555
00:39:03,007 --> 00:39:06,773
<i>They tie themselves in horrible knots</i>
<i>They come in stripes or polka dots</i>

556
00:39:06,844 --> 00:39:10,871
<i>Beware, beware</i>
<i>be a very wary bear</i>

557
00:40:47,278 --> 00:40:50,509
<i>They're extraordinary</i>
<i>so better be wary</i>

558
00:40:50,581 --> 00:40:54,847
<i>Because they come in every</i>
<i>shape and size, size, size, size</i>

